TRI HITA KARANA — Philosophy Images
=====================================

3 images representing the three principles of Tri Hita Karana.
These appear in the Philosophy section on the homepage and About page.

SIZE:     800 × 600 px  (4:3 ratio)
FORMAT:   JPG

FILES NEEDED (name them exactly as shown)
-----------------------------------------

palemahan-nature.jpg
  Principle: Harmony with Nature (Palemahan)
  Content:   Bali landscape, rice terraces, ocean, jungle, ecosystem,
             or any image evoking harmony with the natural world.

pawongan-people.jpg
  Principle: Harmony with People (Pawongan)
  Content:   Community gathering, collaborative work, people connecting,
             team at MDG, local craftspeople, or workshop group.

parahyangan-spirit.jpg
  Principle: Harmony with Spirit (Parahyangan)
  Content:   Balinese temple, offering ceremony, spiritual practice,
             or a contemplative/meaningful moment.

NOTES
-----
- These images can be slightly darker/moodier than the people photos.
- They should feel poetic and evocative, not purely documentary.
- Avoid overly touristy or clichéd Bali imagery if possible.
